rebirth process
symbolic imagery
dialogue structure
spiritual practices
recurring metaphysical vocabulary
2. Master Structural Reading

Unlike Agrippa (encyclopedia) or Dee (diaries), the Corpus Hermeticum is not one continuous treatise. It is a sequence of increasingly intimate initiatory dialogues.

The progression is roughly:

cosmic revelation
definition of God
creation
human condition
intellect
ignorance
rebirth
ethical transformation
contemplative ascent

The movement is:

vision → explanation → psychology → practice → initiation → deification

This progression should govern the companion volume.

