Function: Reforms the operator before power.
Priority: A.
Essay territory: purification as technology.

Holy Guardian Angel

Surface topic: central angelic revelation.
Function: Provides divine mediation and true authority.
Priority: A+.
Essay territory: the operation’s heart.

Command of Spirits

Surface topic: spirits, hierarchy, oaths.
Function: Subordinates lower powers after angelic contact.
Priority: A.
Essay territory: authority after encounter.

Magic Squares

Surface topic: letter squares for practical effects.
Function: Shows the applied, technical remainder of the system.
Priority: B/A.
Essay territory: power under structure.

